<template>
  <button id="bigBtn" class="btn btn-secondary m-4 shadow bg-white border rounded" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="bottom" title="This click will change your life.">
      {{ createSchedule }}
  </button>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "ServiceOption",
  data() {
    return {
      createSchedule: "Create a schedule"
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
#bigBtn {
  height: 20vw;
  width: 20vw;
}
</style>
